0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a>宣布，由于负责人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grian-chatten">Grian Chatten</a>受伤而取消了整个南美各地的几次巡回演出，在下面找到更多。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-its-amazing-to-be-young-new-single-video-interview-new-music-3839968"><strong>Fontaines DC告诉我们有关美丽的新单曲“这真是太好了”，接下来是什么</strong></a></li></ul><p>今天（3月18日），查滕（Chatten）访问了乐队的官方Instagram帐户，<a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/fontainesband/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">通过Instagram故事分享声明</a>，他透露自己遭受了椎间盘突出，需要“紧急医疗护理”。结果，Fontaines DC的接下来五个日期被取消。</p><p>查滕写道：“我很沮丧地宣布，由于椎间盘突出，我们必须明天晚上在墨西哥取消我们在墨西哥的演出，以及即将在智利，阿根廷，巴西和哥伦比亚举行的约会。”</p><p>他继续说：“多年来，我真的很高兴能在墨西哥城来这里，无法在舞台上上台，但是今天我被告知我需要紧急的医疗服务，我们非常感谢您的所有支持，我全心全意，我很抱歉为您效力。” </p><figure id="attachment_3839897" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839897" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839897" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Fontaines D.C.的Grian Chatten在Leeds Festival 2024的第三天在主要舞台上演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fontaines@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839897" class="wp-caption-text"> Fontaines DC的Grian Chatten在2024年利兹节的第三天在主要舞台上演出。贷方：Matthew Baker/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在撰写本文时，看来这些节目已被完全取消，因为没有迹象表明乐队正在重新安排五场演出以进行以后的日期。</p><p>乐队的南美巡回演出日期的取消是在乐队本月初结束<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-2025-japan-australia-and-new-zealand-tour-dates-3805334">日本，澳大利亚和新西兰巡回演唱会</a>之后不久。乐队接下来将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-2025-us-headline-tour-3807704">在4月中旬开始他们的北美巡回演出</a>，尽管目前尚无关于格莱恩·查顿（Grian Chatten）受伤是否会影响这些日期的消息。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="与Fontaines D.C.的Grian Chatten在家：“我们的个性比我们发出的声音更大”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cAncWquXDE8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>今年晚些时候，乐队将于今年夏天返回欧洲和英国进行一场巨大的户外标题表演和节日露面，包括7月5日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-huge-2025-show-at-londons-finsbury-park-buy-tickets-3780336">伦敦的Finsbury Park</a>售罄，7月13日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-dc-announce-newcastle-summer-2025-show-english-teacher-buy-tickets-3817788">纽卡斯尔</a>，7月30日的纽卡斯尔， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-add-huge-cardiff-castle-show-to-summer-2025-uk-tour-plans-3806310">加的夫城堡</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-massive-2025-manchester-show-at-wythenshawe-park-3797642">曼彻斯特的Wythenshawe Park</a> 8月15日<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedi